            <h3 class="font-semibold text-left mb-3">Stud Poker Rules</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Both 5-Card Stud and 7-Card Stud are classic poker variants where players build their best hand from a combination of face-down "hole cards" and face-up "door cards" dealt over several rounds, with betting after each new card. The primary difference lies in the total number of cards dealt to each player (five vs. seven) and how many are hidden versus revealed. The goal remains the same: to form the best five-card poker hand.</p>
